guild.description:
Keep up to date with current events with this guild. If you feel you're Out Of The Loop, ask your question about whatever it is here!
 
Rules:

– Be Civil

– Title must be a current and unbiased question.

– Post should include context.

– Try not to ask something that has already been asked recently.

– Don't be biased with answers.
